caption.p: Characteristics of an RRV outbreak among Australian Defence Force (ADF) personnel during and after training in Shoalwater Bay Training Area (SWBTA), northeastern Australia, 2016. A) RRV attack rates among 3 ADF units. B) Routes of ADF units during exercises in SWBTA. C) Timeline of outbreak. EPA, epidemic polyarthritis; RRV, Ross River virus; UOTF, urban operation training facility.
